Text: Picnic Table Cc Barry Sorry to hear you have been sick Hope you are feeling better We have no plans to be up this week end but we are discussing a work day for a week end soon You are welcome to use the picnic table this week end or anytime I submitted the estimate of damages to the District Attoneys office soon after I asked you for it but havent heard anything on the final outcome of the case Conrad Original Message From barry crouch mailto Sent Thursday October PM To Subject conrad if you all arent coming up this week end may i borrow your picknic table this saturday things are fine around here have been sick for the past month we are trying to get the calf to the butcher then i will have to start all over how did it come out with cloud will see you later barry mary Get your FREE download of MSN Explorer at intlasp winmaildat
